  m_text: 'Humans are coming to take the magic from the tree of magic!


    drag
    and drop towers from the top right scroll onto sections of the lane to place
    towers and defend the tree.

    Each tower has a mana cost that must be paid
    every second, seen on their profile card (makred by a star)

    Use unicorn
    bunnies to increase your magic gain (but they can only be summoned once every
    30 seconds

    Mouse over a placed tower and press backspace to dismiss a tower,
    you will stop using mana on it as a result.


    Don''t let the humans get through
    and don''t run out of magic!'
